{"tid":467951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生組織今早20院校門外派港獨傳單","createTime":"2017-11-14T03:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T04:59:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"403ed0805837d1b712699c59aa78e5363d5cd38c","tid":467951,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T03:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510628980_177b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510628980_177b.png&h=f820d8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「香港民族陣綫」今早8時許在facebook表示，與學生組織「學生動源」，今晨於港九新界約20間院校門外，派發播獨傳單，表明「要將獨立呼聲傳遍校園」，包括元朗一間津助英文中學。學生動源則指，沙田有中學生自發於校門派發港獨傳單，希望將港獨聲音「打入校園每一個角落」。<br />\n<br />\n陣綫指，自本港陷於內地「匪手」以來，民生、法治等範疇無一倖免大倒退，學界受洗腦教材荼毒甚深，內地人更來港搶奪學位，「作為香港未來的主人，學界更應切身體會到，只有香港獨立才有未來可言」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171114/57456151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F57456151&d=DLcSJ3at4d3q9zJfdG0Pmf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3be3da33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F57456151&h=6356f258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171114/57456151</a>"},{"pid":"8f1bd7794e403992312a3df4cd36836e9b275a1d","tid":467951,"uid":41356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"中學都叫院校好似有啲奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我唔識嘢"},{"pid":"9cb7ce0c811038dfb75917a16b3b798c6a86fe62","tid":467951,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:38:16.000Z","msg":"支持民陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53f70ee85abd6f624c472336d3a0a42dfcd7c3b","tid":467951,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學都叫院校好似有啲奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我唔識嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學都叫書院好怪，可能我唔識野"}]}